{"tid":1481772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"閩    粵    人    不    等    於    漢     人","createTime":"2019-08-17T23:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:25:21.000Z","uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eba5708aeece4f3a60a4d99a1d1abf7c96b4abf8","tid":1481772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:23:31.000Z","msg":"&lt;再轉PTT&gt;<br />\n閩粵人不等於漢人 <br />\n <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7ErazO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7ErazO5.jpg&h=89db5eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3OKzY1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3OKzY1H.jpg&h=0521dc19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jkA3X71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjkA3X71.jpg&h=974e9ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林媽利教授的馬偕團隊根據台灣人的血緣做出研究，發現多數&quot;台灣人&quot;其實是平埔族與閩 粵移民的混血，而閩粵移民其實是漢化的越人，並非我們一直以為的&quot;中原漢人&quot;。 這套說法並沒有寫入教科書中，所以多數人仍以為，閩粵移民也是漢人，所以也應該是中 國人，而不知道，閩粵人其實早就拋棄了自己的越人文化，被漢文化同化。 可悲的是，平埔人也以為自己是漢人，然後高山族以為漢化的平埔是閩人，然後一併厭惡 之。這就表現在高山原民寧願把票給國民黨，而不願給本土、操閩南語(=漢化平埔)的民 進黨。 在這樣的基礎上，台灣的母語運動追尋的是誰的母語？台灣人使用的漢語文應該怎樣定位 ，都是個值得深思的問題。 但台灣人絕對不是純粹的漢人。而台灣人是不是中國人，就要看你覺得中國人的定義是什 麼了。 補~ 想深入了解就自己去翻這本書，我整理的內容有限，文本就在那裡，請自行檢視運用。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UfYf1WY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUfYf1WY.jpg&h=5c42f1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qSnQ38H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqSnQ38H.jpg&h=c40276fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://bbstop.amassly.com/post/Gossiping_1LH8CpVu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbstop.amassly.com%2Fpost%2FGossiping_1LH8CpVu&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1CHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=6a917d9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bbstop.amassly.com/post/Gossiping_1LH8CpVu</a>"},{"pid":"a78a887a07e043bdf07e3a217848774f95c6c13f","tid":1481772,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d157de74cfde32f47a4b69de232d54a77e804c4","tid":1481772,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65584968e2db0be62c8211707fe1d5f4fe827a25","tid":1481772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9bf354d35ad0dee0287069598934b007bcb8d8","tid":1481772,"uid":229508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:42:45.000Z","msg":"南方人不是漢人"},{"pid":"dd4a38aad35c66d8c4ff7cff676953763850de25","tid":1481772,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:46:28.000Z","msg":"自秦漢中原人開始侵殖閩粤<br />\n閩粤人原係百越族<br />\n跟越南 台灣 東南亞原居民係近親<br />\n跟中原人係遠鄰"},{"pid":"794c069af94eefe663c5f11e2457541688ec0f16","tid":1481772,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T00:01:04.000Z","msg":"有冇圖show下兩種人面貌分別"},{"pid":"b93abdeaf55f1909de2d757a981e51cb5b840d03","tid":1481772,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T00:01:45.000Z","msg":"而家越南人又係咪百越人"},{"pid":"d74f8a4c733b1207464f5a599948fdc778aeeafc","tid":1481772,"uid":103513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T00:12:21.000Z","msg":"真正近親根本係越南人<br />\n漢人當年只不過係侵略者<br />\n但越人文化水平低過漢人又係真<br />\n所以先咁多越人自稱漢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb827f8a028588d3d7578c3f57df38d768fee419","tid":1481772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b776327de97c06c802c3